  "detailed_description": "<h1>From the developer</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was developed by one person, <strong>not recommended for those who require high quality (or otherwise)</strong> (I can only optimize slowly)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any problems you encounter in the game can be told in the community, I will solve it for you as soon as possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't buy or download if you have a high demand for the game's image quality (or otherwise)</strong></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"FMTC\" is a multiplayer online shooting game (TPS+FPS) with 2Tap gameplay. Choose the right landing spot, select skills that suit you, and search for weapons, ammunition, armor, vehicles, and other equipment. One shot to break the helmet, the second shot to kill with a headshot, two shots to eliminate enemies. Every moment is a matter of life and death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
